vzpkg2 (0.9.2) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fix bogus create of /vz/template on Debian.

  * Create /var/lib/rpm if necessary work around Debian install bug.

  * Do a filesystem sync before creating tarball to eliminate tar warnings.

